name: adidas Yeezy Boost 350 V2 Cinder
description: Jordan Brand brings back another popular release with the Jordan 6 DMP (2020), now available on StockX. The original Defining Moments Package debuted in 2006 as a tribute to Michael Jordan’s pair of three-peat championships in the 1990’s with the Chicago Bulls. This Jordan 6 colorway was included in the package alongside an Air Jordan 11 in a similar colorway. This is the first time that these sneakers have been retroed.
